HEADWORD: Macrocosm
<hw>Mac"ro*cosm</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Macro-</ets>
+ Gr. <?/ the world: cf. F. <ets>macrocosme</ets>.]</ety> <def>The great
world; that part of the universe which is exterior to man; -- contrasted
with <xex>microcosm</xex>, or man. See <er>Microcosm</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Macrocosmic</ent>⟦br⟧
